that Shen Yu

275
00:11:42,050 --> 00:11:43,890
is indeed a pawn of Minister Shi.

276
00:11:44,340 --> 00:11:46,220
What should we do next?

277
00:11:46,980 --> 00:11:48,650
Should we tell the Ban family the truth?

278
00:11:49,010 --> 00:11:49,700
No need.

279
00:11:49,940 --> 00:11:51,250
It concerns His Majesty
and the Tiger Tally.

280
00:11:52,460 --> 00:11:53,740
The less people know, the better.

281
00:11:54,370 --> 00:11:55,130
Yes.

282
00:11:56,580 --> 00:11:58,890
You can’t even answer
such a simple question.

283
00:11:59,530 --> 00:12:00,290
Sure enough,

284
00:12:00,530 --> 00:12:01,980
we have nothing to say.

285
00:12:02,460 --> 00:12:03,530
I don’t have any ill intention.

286
00:12:04,740 --> 00:12:06,340
I just care about you.

287
00:12:09,820 --> 00:12:11,500
We are neither relatives nor friends.

288
00:12:11,530 --> 00:12:13,050
