for a long time.

308
00:12:55,650 --> 00:12:57,050
I have already taken you as…

309
00:13:00,770 --> 00:13:01,580
As a friend.

310
00:13:02,890 --> 00:13:04,820
What’s wrong with a friend
caring about another friend?

311
00:13:05,370 --> 00:13:06,410
A friend?

312
00:13:07,500 --> 00:13:09,370
That’s from a model for all scholars?

313
00:13:09,370 --> 00:13:10,530
He is too bad at talking.

314
00:13:10,530 --> 00:13:11,130
Exactly.

315
00:13:13,170 --> 00:13:15,010
There is nothing wrong
with what Young Master said.

316
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:16,980
I don’t know if
there is anything wrong.

317
00:13:17,050 --> 00:13:18,010
But I know

318
00:13:18,170 --> 00:13:19,860
Baroness is going to snap.

319
00:13:22,170 --> 00:13:23,130
Count Cheng’an.

320
00:13:24,340 --> 00:13:25,820
What’s that explanation?

321
00:13:26,170 --> 00:13:27,940
It’s obvious that you are
ruining my engagement.

322
00:13:28,100 --> 00:13:29,890
Now you tell me

323
00:13:29,890 --> 00:13:31,500
that you only take me as a friend!

324
00:13:31,620 --> 00:13:32,650
Baroness, calm down.

325
00:13:32,740 --> 00:13:33,740
Let me explain.

326
00:13:34,460 --> 00:13:36,250
I didn’t handle it properly about Wang.

327
00:13:36,860 --> 00:13:37,770
But it was urgent.

328
00:13:38,050 --> 00:13:38,770
Wang was taken away intentionally

329
00:13:38,770 --> 00:13:40,100
by someone.

330
00:13:40,740 --> 00:13:42,250
I had to take the risk.

331
00:13:42,500 --> 00:13:43,460
I hope you can understand me.

332
00:13:43,530 --> 00:13:44,500
You still lied to me!

333
00:13:44,940 --> 00:13:46,410
And you’re worse than Shen Yu!

334
00:13:46,700 --> 00:13:47,370
I was...

335
00:13:49,740 --> 00:13:51,340
I was also thinking for you.

336
00:13:52,980 --> 00:13:55,050
