337
00:13:55,170 --> 00:13:56,340
even he deceived you?

338
00:13:57,410 --> 00:13:59,100
I’ll marry your whole family!

339
00:13:59,220 --> 00:14:00,410
There is only me in my family!

340
00:14:04,740 --> 00:14:06,580
Was that a swearing?

341
00:14:07,370 --> 00:14:08,530
I don’t want to waste time
talking to you.

342
00:14:08,980 --> 00:14:09,940
Let me ask you again.

343
00:14:10,860 --> 00:14:12,100
Are you afraid of me being cheated

344
00:14:12,700 --> 00:14:13,980
