345
00:14:18,890 --> 00:14:19,860
Good question.

346
00:14:20,130 --> 00:14:21,500
This is a deadly question.

347
00:14:21,980 --> 00:14:23,010
It’s easy.

348
00:14:23,050 --> 00:14:24,250
Of course he is afraid of her
being cheated.

349
00:14:26,170 --> 00:14:27,220
Although I’m not that clever,

350
00:14:27,460 --> 00:14:29,820
I’m sure this is not the right answer.

351
00:14:30,740 --> 00:14:31,370
Exactly.

352
00:14:33,980 --> 00:14:36,050
Forget it. I can’t get anything
from you.

353
00:14:36,460 --> 00:14:38,130
I’d better ask the God.

354
00:14:39,340 --> 00:14:39,890
Let’s go.

355
00:14:43,500 --> 00:14:45,010
Are you made of wood?

356
00:14:48,130 --> 00:14:49,620
She is talking about your Young Master.

357
00:14:52,250 --> 00:14:53,010
Ban Heng!

358
00:14:53,620 --> 00:14:54,340
Come and lead the horse!

359
00:14:54,460 --> 00:14:55,220
Coming!

360
00:15:01,860 --> 00:15:02,530
Let’s go.

361
00:15:02,530 --> 00:15:03,100
Hua.

362
00:15:05,530 --> 00:15:06,290
Be good.

363
00:15:07,100 --> 00:15:08,620
Am I afraid of her being cheated

364
00:15:09,940 --> 00:15:11,220
or her getting married?

365
00:15:12,740 --> 00:15:15,580
Baroness Ban, in fact...

366
00:15:26,340 --> 00:15:27,530
I don’t want to waste time
talking to you.

367
00:15:27,700 --> 00:15:28,700
Let me ask you again.

368
00:15:29,530 --> 00:15:30,740
Are you afraid of me being cheated

369
00:15:31,410 --> 00:15:32,530
or me getting married?

370
00:15:36,530 --> 00:15:37,740
Young Master

371
00:15:38,170 --> 00:15:39,700
has been reading this page
for more than two hours.

372
00:15:43,860 --> 00:15:44,740
Woman

373
00:15:45,620 --> 00:15:47,770
is the hardest book in the world.

374
00:15:48,700 --> 00:15:50,130
Mr. Rong, hush up.

375
00:15:50,500 --> 00:15:52,460
Young Master won’t
fall in love with Baroness Ban.

376
00:15:53,500 --> 00:15:54,290
Jiu.

377
00:15:55,370 --> 00:15:57,980
Feelings are not something
you can control.

378
00:15:59,860 --> 00:16:01,650
Come on, open the door. Let me in.

379
00:16:12,340 --> 00:16:14,370
Young Master, it’s cold now.

380
00:16:14,370 --> 00:16:15,220
Have some ginseng tea.

381
00:16:16,170 --> 00:16:18,650
I saw that you were lost in thought.

382
00:16:19,050 --> 00:16:20,170
Do you have something on mind?

383
00:16:22,170 --> 00:16:22,890
There is nothing.

384
00:16:23,740 --> 00:16:24,740
That’s good.

385
00:16:25,460 --> 00:16:28,250
If it wasn’t for your help,

386
00:16:29,410 --> 00:16:30,980
Baroness Ban would be
deceived by Shen Yu,

387
00:16:31,370 --> 00:16:32,890
and it would be hard for you
to meet again.

388
00:16:36,740 --> 00:16:37,530
Young Master.

389
00:16:38,340 --> 00:16:39,860
I get along well with that kid.

390
00:16:40,290 --> 00:16:41,460
Why don’t you find some time

391
00:16:41,820 --> 00:16:43,290
to invite her here for dinner?

392
00:16:47,410 --> 00:16:48,130
No need.

393
00:16:51,010 --> 00:16:52,050
I don’t think Baroness Ban

394
00:16:52,820 --> 00:16:54,050
will come here again.

395
00:16:56,650 --> 00:16:57,460
That’s outrageous!

396
00:16:58,940 --> 00:17:00,250
I’ve been planning this for so long!

397
00:17:00,650 --> 00:17:02,770
Now it was all ruined
by a few whippings of Baroness Ban?

398
00:17:04,820 --> 00:17:05,890
That Shen Yu

399
00:17:06,170 --> 00:17:08,410
is indeed good for nothing!

400
00:17:09,940 --> 00:17:12,500
It’s my fault for not
keeping an eye on him.

401
00:17:12,740 --> 00:17:14,330
He is still from the countryside.

402
00:17:14,420 --> 00:17:16,220
He doesn’t know how important it is.

403
00:17:16,420 --> 00:17:17,180
Never mind.

404
00:17:17,810 --> 00:17:20,570
Now we’ve lost Shen Yu as our contact.

405
00:17:22,610 --> 00:17:25,980
How to look for the Tiger Tally now?

406
00:17:26,570 --> 00:17:27,610
Do you have any idea?

407
00:17:27,770 --> 00:17:31,850
It’s too important. We need
to give it further thought.

408
00:17:32,290 --> 00:17:33,980
His Majesty has lost his patience!

409
00:17:34,500 --> 00:17:35,140
Sir.

410
00:17:35,460 --> 00:17:37,700
Why don’t you tell on the Ban family

411
00:17:38,330 --> 00:17:39,700
to His Majesty in court tomorrow

412
00:17:39,940 --> 00:17:41,980
