whipping Shen Yu in public?

413
00:17:43,220 --> 00:17:44,530
Shen Yu cheated on her first.

414
00:17:45,140 --> 00:17:47,610
It’s understandable that Baroness Ban

415
00:17:48,050 --> 00:17:49,090
was mad at him and taught him a lesson.

416
00:17:49,770 --> 00:17:52,380
Let’s not do such things.

417
00:17:53,700 --> 00:17:55,700
Young Master, you’re back.

418
00:17:58,460 --> 00:18:00,740
Jin has a point.

419
00:18:01,330 --> 00:18:02,220
Mr. Wu.

420
00:18:02,420 --> 00:18:04,420
Things like kicking a person
when he is down,

421
00:18:04,770 --> 00:18:06,090
