in a profound and sensational way,

466
00:19:42,980 --> 00:19:45,220
and strike a blow at the Ban family?

467
00:19:45,530 --> 00:19:46,530
Yeah.

468
00:19:51,180 --> 00:19:51,630
Okay!

469
00:19:51,640 --> 00:20:01,680
<i>Memorial to the throne Please punish
Baroness Ban for whipping people</i>

470
00:20:01,810 --> 00:20:02,660
It’s excellent.

471
00:20:02,660 --> 00:20:04,250
Your Grace is good at writing.

472
00:20:04,250 --> 00:20:05,740
Your words are fascinating.

473
00:20:06,330 --> 00:20:07,290
More than that.

474
00:20:07,290 --> 00:20:09,660
Your Grace explained
the profound truth in simple language.

475
00:20:10,250 --> 00:20:11,700
I’m so inferior to you.

476
00:20:12,180 --> 00:20:13,900
We are all depending on you.

477
00:20:14,330 --> 00:20:18,140
When you make a move,
we are all lost in admiration.

478
00:20:18,140 --> 00:20:19,090
Yeah, exactly.

479
00:20:19,090 --> 00:20:21,010
You are excellent.

480
00:20:21,180 --> 00:20:22,500
Well, Mr. Song,

481
00:20:22,770 --> 00:20:24,180
your skill of flattering

482
00:20:24,330 --> 00:20:27,660
is much better than your writing.

483
00:20:29,700 --> 00:20:30,660
Everyone.

484
00:20:31,330 --> 00:20:33,090
I’ll rely on you

485
00:20:33,220 --> 00:20:34,740
to solve our Xie family’s issue
with the Ban family.

486
00:20:34,770 --> 00:20:35,610
We are here for you.

487
00:20:35,610 --> 00:20:38,500
You must help
our Xie family get justice.

488
00:20:38,940 --> 00:20:39,770
Sure.

489
00:20:39,770 --> 00:20:42,330
My daughter was just

490
00:20:42,500 --> 00:20:43,700
engaged to the Second Prince.

491
00:20:44,180 --> 00:20:46,940
There are many things I need to prepare.

492
00:20:46,980 --> 00:20:48,740
Your Grace, you are so polite.

493
00:20:49,330 --> 00:20:51,770
Now the wedding of
the Second Prince and your daughter

494
00:20:51,770 --> 00:20:52,610
is the most important thing.

495
00:20:52,770 --> 00:20:54,980
Don’t worry about the Ban family.

496
00:20:55,050 --> 00:20:56,380
Just leave it to us.

497
00:20:56,570 --> 00:20:57,250
Yeah.

498
00:20:57,460 --> 00:20:58,980
After your daughter
marries into the royal family,

499
00:20:59,140 --> 00:21:01,500
we hope Your Grace can help us.

500
00:21:01,740 --> 00:21:03,330
Yes, thank you, Your Grace.

501
00:21:09,460 --> 00:21:11,330
