514
00:21:50,900 --> 00:21:53,810
The people out there all think...

515
00:21:55,420 --> 00:21:56,420
Think what?

516
00:21:56,770 --> 00:21:59,700
You Majesty, I dare not say.

517
00:22:01,050 --> 00:22:03,290
Go ahead, I won’t punish you.

518
00:22:05,740 --> 00:22:07,500
They think that Daye

519
00:22:07,770 --> 00:22:09,220
is ruled by the Ban family now.

520
00:22:10,050 --> 00:22:12,220
Mr. Song, you can drink alcohol
as you want,

521
00:22:12,850 --> 00:22:14,090
but you can’t talk nonsense!

522
00:22:15,570 --> 00:22:18,090
That’s just how the commoners
think about it.

523
00:22:18,420 --> 00:22:19,810
Why are you nervous about it?

524
00:22:19,980 --> 00:22:21,180
Count Xie is right.

525
00:22:22,220 --> 00:22:23,010
Your Majesty.

526
00:22:23,700 --> 00:22:27,530
Please stop the spread
of rumors outside.

527
00:22:28,050 --> 00:22:29,500
That’s ridiculous.

528
00:22:29,900 --> 00:22:30,570
Your Majesty.

529
00:22:30,660 --> 00:22:33,330
This is not the only trouble
Ban Hua made.

530
00:22:33,770 --> 00:22:34,980
If you keep tolerating her,

531
00:22:34,980 --> 00:22:36,770
your prestige will be lost.

532
00:22:38,140 --> 00:22:38,940
Your Majesty.

533
00:22:39,330 --> 00:22:40,330
In my opinion,

534
00:22:40,900 --> 00:22:43,290
it was not that Baroness Ban
whipped an imperial officer.

535
00:22:43,660 --> 00:22:46,330
It was a woman who was cheated
beating a ruthless man.

536
00:22:47,380 --> 00:22:49,090
Shen Yu was engaged before.

537
00:22:49,570 --> 00:22:51,140
