of the Ban family.

538
00:22:51,460 --> 00:22:52,740
He abandoned his dutiful wife

539
00:22:53,050 --> 00:22:54,050
and tried to marry Baroness Ban.

540
00:22:54,570 --> 00:22:55,660
From this point of view,

541
00:22:55,810 --> 00:22:57,050
he is an immoral person.

542
00:22:57,530 --> 00:22:59,220
Baroness Ban did nothing wrong.

543
00:22:59,220 --> 00:23:00,900
Count Cheng’an tried to excuse her
with fancy words.

544
00:23:01,140 --> 00:23:02,330
But it can’t change the fact

545
00:23:02,330 --> 00:23:05,330
that Ban Hua whipped
an imperial officer in public!

546
00:23:05,460 --> 00:23:08,500
Baroness Ban is rude and extravagant.

547
00:23:08,770 --> 00:23:10,420
Count Cheng’an,
you defend her like this.

548
00:23:10,980 --> 00:23:11,810
Could it be

