550
00:23:15,290 --> 00:23:17,010
Your Grace, Mr. Song.

551
00:23:18,180 --> 00:23:19,850
You two insist that Baroness Ban
should be punished.

552
00:23:20,250 --> 00:23:21,140
Are you trying

553
00:23:21,180 --> 00:23:23,290
to cover for an immoral person?

554
00:23:23,900 --> 00:23:25,090
Well, Count Cheng’an.

555
00:23:25,610 --> 00:23:27,610
His Grace and Mr. Song

556
00:23:27,660 --> 00:23:29,330
are aiming at facts, not people.

557
00:23:29,330 --> 00:23:31,900
Baroness Ban happened to be
involved in it.

558
00:23:32,530 --> 00:23:34,290
If it was someone else,

559
00:23:34,770 --> 00:23:37,330
these two ministers will still
vigorously offer their advice.

560
00:23:37,460 --> 00:23:40,380
Count Xie, I know your intention.

561
00:23:40,380 --> 00:23:41,090
What’s my intention?

562
00:23:41,090 --> 00:23:43,090
You are seeking personal revenge
in the name of public interests.

563
00:23:43,220 --> 00:23:45,180
You did it for your blind son.

564
00:23:45,460 --> 00:23:46,220
You lost the money
and your son is blind!

565
00:23:46,220 --> 00:23:47,570
That’s why you try to hurt Hua!

566
00:23:47,570 --> 00:23:48,500
Well, Marquis Jingting.

567
00:23:48,500 --> 00:23:49,770
What do you mean by that?

568
00:23:49,770 --> 00:23:50,900
My son is blind.

569
00:23:50,900 --> 00:23:51,940
You keep mentioning it all the time.

570
00:23:51,940 --> 00:23:53,850
What do you mean?

571
00:23:53,850 --> 00:23:56,010
What do I mean?
You know what I mean!

572
00:23:56,010 --> 00:23:57,330
I don’t know what you mean!

573
00:23:57,330 --> 00:23:58,290
Listen!

574
00:23:58,290 --> 00:23:58,850
-You...!
-You...!

575
00:24:04,090 --> 00:24:04,770
Your Majesty.

576
00:24:04,770 --> 00:24:06,700
I think Shen Yu...

577
00:24:06,700 --> 00:24:09,460
Your Majesty, let alone other things,

578
00:24:10,250 --> 00:24:12,180
the fact that Shen Yu cheated on her

579
00:24:12,740 --> 00:24:15,330
shows the immorality of his behavior.

580
00:24:15,330 --> 00:24:17,810
I think he should be heavily punished.

581
00:24:20,530 --> 00:24:21,290
However,

582
00:24:21,530 --> 00:24:24,090
Ban Hua whipped the imperial officer.

583
00:24:24,610 --> 00:24:26,660
Your Majesty, I heard

584
00:24:26,940 --> 00:24:28,530
that Mr. Shi was there when it happened.

585
00:24:29,660 --> 00:24:30,810
Minister Yan, you misunderstood.

586
00:24:31,530 --> 00:24:33,740
When Shi Jin arrived there,

587
00:24:33,900 --> 00:24:35,090
it was already over.

588
00:24:37,460 --> 00:24:40,500
Shi Jin, since you were at the scene,

589
00:24:41,380 --> 00:24:42,570
tell me your opinion.

590
00:24:44,330 --> 00:24:45,090
Your Majesty.

591
00:24:45,570 --> 00:24:46,940
Although I arrived late,

592
00:24:47,290 --> 00:24:48,570
I also investigated this matter.

593
00:24:48,900 --> 00:24:50,090
According to the people at the scene,

594
00:24:50,290 --> 00:24:51,500
Shen Yu did cheat on her first.

595
00:24:52,050 --> 00:24:53,610
Then Baroness Ban whipped him.

596
00:24:53,770 --> 00:24:55,010
And Baroness Ban said
she would teach that scumbag

597
00:24:55,010 --> 00:24:57,010
a lesson for Your Majesty
when she whipped him.

598
00:24:57,530 --> 00:24:59,940
It shows Baroness Ban’s
respect for Your Majesty.

599
00:25:00,140 --> 00:25:02,500
She also felt angry for Your Majesty
to be blinded by Shen Yu.

600
00:25:03,850 --> 00:25:05,010
Therefore, I think

601
00:25:05,250 --> 00:25:07,740
Baroness Ban has no disrespect
to Your Majesty.

602
00:25:08,250 --> 00:25:09,660
Mr. Shi has a point.

603
00:25:09,980 --> 00:25:11,610
Your Majesty, I think

604
00:25:11,810 --> 00:25:13,220
Shen Yu should be punished.

605
00:25:13,290 --> 00:25:15,050
If people like Shen Yu
take position in court,

606
00:25:15,090 --> 00:25:16,500
I’m afraid it might
hurt the foundation of Daye,

607
00:25:16,660 --> 00:25:18,660
and lose the support of the people.

608
00:25:19,570 --> 00:25:23,250
Your Majesty, Shen Yu
deserves a heavy penalty!

609
00:25:23,530 --> 00:25:24,700
But Baroness Ban

610
00:25:24,700 --> 00:25:26,530
shouldn’t get away with it easily!

611
00:25:28,090 --> 00:25:28,810
Yes.

612
00:25:29,610 --> 00:25:30,290
He has a point.

613
00:25:32,460 --> 00:25:33,740
In the morning court,

614
00:25:34,500 --> 00:25:36,180
they were either asking me
to punish Hua

615
00:25:36,420 --> 00:25:38,010
or asking me to forgive Hua.

616
00:25:38,850 --> 00:25:40,220
In the court of Daye,

617
00:25:40,380 --> 00:25:41,380
isn’t there anything more important

618
00:25:41,380 --> 00:25:42,290
than that?

619
00:25:42,900 --> 00:25:44,010
By the grace of Your Majesty,

620
00:25:44,380 --> 00:25:47,290
Daye is prosperous
and people are at peace.

621
00:25:49,220 --> 00:25:51,250
Princess Royal presents herself!

622
00:25:52,500 --> 00:25:53,850
Why is she here again?

623
00:26:03,810 --> 00:26:05,420
Aunt, why are you here?

624
00:26:06,420 --> 00:26:08,500
I deserve a death penalty!

625
00:26:08,500 --> 00:26:10,220
-Please punish me.
-Don’t.

626
00:26:10,660 --> 00:26:11,850
Aunt, don’t do that.

627
00:26:11,850 --> 00:26:13,140
Please stand up.

628
00:26:13,810 --> 00:26:15,460
I neglected to discipline my child

629
00:26:16,090 --> 00:26:18,530
and caused many troubles
to the court of Daye.

630
00:26:18,570 --> 00:26:21,610
Your Majesty, please give me
a death penalty now!

631
00:26:21,700 --> 00:26:22,700
Aunt.

632
00:26:22,850 --> 00:26:23,380
You...

633
00:26:23,380 --> 00:26:25,570
You mustn’t say such absurd things.

634
00:26:25,900 --> 00:26:28,180
I can’t live without you.

635
00:26:31,050 --> 00:26:32,980
No matter how I cherish her,

636
00:26:33,810 --> 00:26:35,810
I can’t put you in a difficult position.

637
00:26:36,660 --> 00:26:38,700
I can only blame my husband
for his early death.

638
00:26:39,420 --> 00:26:42,250
I neglected to discipline my children

639
00:26:42,660 --> 00:26:45,610
and caused trouble
for Your Majesty again and again.

640
00:26:45,610 --> 00:26:48,290
Aunt, just listen to me.

641
00:26:49,050 --> 00:26:52,140
No matter it’s Hua’s fault or not,

642
00:26:52,500 --> 00:26:55,530
what I care about the most
is our relationship.

643
00:26:56,460 --> 00:26:58,010
Your Majesty, you are affectionate.

644
00:26:59,330 --> 00:27:01,700
But the people out there are realistic.

645
00:27:02,700 --> 00:27:04,770
Hua whipped an imperial officer
in public.

646
00:27:04,770 --> 00:27:06,290
It’s disrespect to Your Majesty.

647
00:27:06,290 --> 00:27:09,250
This crime is serious enough
to get her beheaded!

648
00:27:09,460 --> 00:27:10,980
Aunt, it’s not that serious.

649
00:27:11,770 --> 00:27:15,050
I watched Hua grow up.

650
00:27:15,460 --> 00:27:16,380
I’ve been...

651
00:27:17,530 --> 00:27:20,330
I’ve been fond of her.

652
00:27:20,460 --> 00:27:22,250
Once Hua got something interesting,

653
00:27:22,330 --> 00:27:24,220
she would show it to me.

654
00:27:24,530 --> 00:27:26,980
I would never believe

655
00:27:26,980 --> 00:27:28,330
that Hua would be disrespectful to me.

656
00:27:29,010 --> 00:27:31,900
Hua is so lucky

657
00:27:32,330 --> 00:27:35,660
to have Your Majesty’s love.

658
00:27:36,740 --> 00:27:40,050
I will handle it.

659
00:27:40,140 --> 00:27:42,140
Don’t worry, Aunt.

660
00:27:43,140 --> 00:27:45,570
Thank you, Your Majesty.

661
00:27:46,140 --> 00:27:47,500
Why do you cry again?

662
00:28:02,460 --> 00:28:03,500
Take care, Aunt.

663
00:28:09,980 --> 00:28:12,530
Are you still in the mood
to give yourself a facial?

664
00:28:14,010 --> 00:28:16,250
It’s a fact that I whipped him.
Whatever will be, will be.

665
00:28:16,500 --> 00:28:18,570
Even to be punished,
I’ll still be beautiful.

666
00:28:19,250 --> 00:28:20,290
Are you sure about that?

667
00:28:21,180 --> 00:28:22,900
The celestial prison is dark and stuffy.

668
00:28:23,570 --> 00:28:24,740
The food is poor there.

669
00:28:24,980 --> 00:28:26,530
And you will eat there, sleep there,
shit there and die there.

670
00:28:26,530 --> 00:28:27,660
You can’t even take

671
00:28:27,660 --> 00:28:28,530
your favorite clothes and jewelry.

672
00:28:29,050 --> 00:28:30,380
Are you sure you can stand it?

673
00:28:31,180 --> 00:28:32,740
His Majesty has always loved me.

674
00:28:33,660 --> 00:28:35,180
He won’t put me in celestial prison.

675
00:28:35,770 --> 00:28:36,500
He will lock me

676
00:28:36,740 --> 00:28:38,180
in the room at most.

677
00:28:38,220 --> 00:28:39,010
Don’t worry.

678
00:28:39,220 --> 00:28:40,610
You are too optimistic.

679
00:28:41,330 --> 00:28:42,050
Well,

680
00:28:42,740 --> 00:28:45,180
the mind of the emperor is
unfathomable as the sea.

681
00:28:45,740 --> 00:28:46,770
Your fate is unpredictable.

682
00:28:47,460 --> 00:28:52,010
Here is the imperial edict!
Baroness Ban, come to receive it!

683
00:28:56,610 --> 00:28:57,570
Baroness Ban.

684
00:28:57,770 --> 00:28:58,460
Yes.

685
00:29:00,330 --> 00:29:01,420
Your face...

686
00:29:02,180 --> 00:29:04,220
These are cucumber slices.

687
00:29:04,380 --> 00:29:06,530
Put it on your face,
and it can enhance your beauty.

688
00:29:07,460 --> 00:29:09,330
Really? Does it really work?

689
00:29:10,420 --> 00:29:11,330
Yes. It’s excellent.

690
00:29:11,850 --> 00:29:12,850
Tell me about it now.

691
00:29:13,090 --> 00:29:14,420
Let’s get down to business first.

692
00:29:14,420 --> 00:29:15,500
I’ll ask someone to send you

693
00:29:15,500 --> 00:29:17,220
a box of it later.

694
00:29:17,420 --> 00:29:19,050
Thank you.

695
00:29:20,660 --> 00:29:22,050
Baroness Ban,
please receive the imperial edict.

696
00:29:24,180 --> 00:29:26,940
By the grace of God, here is
the announcement of His Majesty:

697
00:29:27,250 --> 00:29:31,090
Shen Yu coveted power
and cheated on his marriage contract.

698
00:29:31,460 --> 00:29:34,050
He is removed from his position
and will never be hired again.

699
00:29:34,250 --> 00:29:38,220
Baroness Ban is honest and righteous,
innocent and elegant.

700
00:29:38,330 --> 00:29:41,220
She enforced justice on behalf
of the God and made a contribution.

701
00:29:41,530 --> 00:29:43,700
Now she is made as a countess

702
00:29:45,250 --> 00:29:47,610
with the corvee and tax
of seven hundred households.

703
00:29:47,900 --> 00:29:49,010
Respect this.

704
00:29:50,610 --> 00:29:51,660
Thank you for your grace!

705
00:29:56,660 --> 00:29:58,140
Congratulations, Countess Ban.

706
00:29:58,140 --> 00:29:59,850
I’ll leave now.

707
00:30:07,460 --> 00:30:09,050
Innocent and elegant?

708
00:30:10,810 --> 00:30:11,700
The minister
who wrote the imperial edict

709
00:30:12,770 --> 00:30:14,140
is getting better

710
00:30:14,140 --> 00:30:15,500
at telling lies.

711
00:30:18,810 --> 00:30:19,420
Go on.

712
00:30:25,850 --> 00:30:26,570
This is...

713
00:30:26,850 --> 00:30:27,420
What?

714
00:30:27,900 --> 00:30:29,700
His Majesty is that partial to her?

715
00:30:30,380 --> 00:30:32,900
His Majesty ordered to remove
Shen Yu from his position.

716
00:30:33,140 --> 00:30:34,010
What drugs did the Ban family

717
00:30:34,010 --> 00:30:35,610
feed His Majesty?

718
00:30:36,180 --> 00:30:37,850
Not only did he not punish Ban Hua,

719
00:30:38,050 --> 00:30:39,380
he even gave her a reward.

720
00:30:39,740 --> 00:30:41,810
Father, why don’t we get someone
to ask about it?

721
00:30:42,010 --> 00:30:44,500
What’s their secret
to fawn upon His Majesty?

722
00:30:45,050 --> 00:30:46,530
Stop bothering the Ban family.

723
00:30:46,530 --> 00:30:47,740
We can’t get anything good from it.

724
00:30:47,740 --> 00:30:48,530
Stop talking!

725
00:30:49,250 --> 00:30:50,770
You are the most useless person
in our family!

726
00:30:50,770 --> 00:30:51,530
Do you know that?

727
00:30:51,900 --> 00:30:54,530
If you didn’t change your confession
in the last minute,

728
00:30:54,700 --> 00:30:55,770
how could the Ban family
become like this now?

729
00:30:55,770 --> 00:30:57,290
They would’ve been over a long time ago!

730
00:30:57,420 --> 00:30:59,660
Can’t you still see it?

731
00:30:59,850 --> 00:31:01,290
With the Princess Royal behind them,

732
00:31:01,290 --> 00:31:03,290
nothing will happen to the Ban family.

733
00:31:03,290 --> 00:31:05,660
No matter what you do,
it will all be in vain.

734
00:31:05,660 --> 00:31:07,500
You! You’re pissing me off!

735
00:31:07,940 --> 00:31:08,850
If you keep pissing me off,

736
00:31:08,940 --> 00:31:10,380
the other eye of yours
will also be blind!

737
00:31:10,380 --> 00:31:10,980
Blind?

738
00:31:10,980 --> 00:31:12,660
Qilin, stop.

739
00:31:12,980 --> 00:31:14,460
I’m telling the truth!

740
00:31:14,570 --> 00:31:15,940
You want me to deceive myself?

741
00:31:16,140 --> 00:31:17,500
I might as well be totally blind!

742
00:31:17,740 --> 00:31:18,330
You...!

743
00:31:18,330 --> 00:31:19,530
Get back here! He is…!

744
00:31:19,530 --> 00:31:21,380
Father, calm down.

745
00:31:21,530 --> 00:31:22,900
Qilin is right.

746
00:31:23,180 --> 00:31:24,330
With the Princess Royal being there,

747
00:31:24,530 --> 00:31:27,010
His Majesty can’t do anything
to the Ban family.

748
00:31:27,140 --> 00:31:28,180
Don’t be mad at it.

749
00:31:29,850 --> 00:31:30,980
It’s upsetting.

750
00:31:32,500 --> 00:31:33,460
Strangely enough,

751
00:31:33,570 --> 00:31:36,810
the Shi family never meddled
in the affairs in court.

752
00:31:37,220 --> 00:31:40,050
This time he took the side
of the Ban family.

753
00:31:41,460 --> 00:31:42,250
There must be

754
00:31:44,770 --> 00:31:46,330
something strange about it.

755
00:31:57,850 --> 00:31:59,420
Jin, have some rest.

756
00:32:04,700 --> 00:32:07,460
I heard that you spoke up
for Countess Ban

757
00:32:07,660 --> 00:32:09,090
and made the ministers speechless.

758
00:32:09,700 --> 00:32:10,420
It’s not a big deal.

759
00:32:11,180 --> 00:32:12,380
I was telling the truth.

760
00:32:13,570 --> 00:32:16,010
Speaking of that,
the Ban family is really lucky.

761
00:32:16,180 --> 00:32:17,700
They got good out of misfortune
again and again.

762
00:32:17,740 --> 00:32:19,050
They are really lucky.

763
00:32:19,660 --> 00:32:20,660
Countess Ban got herself
in trouble twice

764
00:32:20,660 --> 00:32:22,010
because of her engagement.

765
00:32:23,250 --> 00:32:24,420
Fortunately, Countess Ban
is straightforward.

766
00:32:25,010 --> 00:32:26,330
If it was some other ordinary woman,

767
00:32:27,050 --> 00:32:28,500
she wouldn’t know how to deal with it.

768
00:32:30,330 --> 00:32:34,290
You seem to admire
Countess Ban a lot.

769
00:32:35,460 --> 00:32:36,610
Why do you say that?

770
00:32:37,380 --> 00:32:38,940
As a military commander,

771
00:32:39,010 --> 00:32:41,140
you’ve been admiring
Old General Ban since you were young.

772
00:32:41,700 --> 00:32:44,850
Although Countess Ban is not literate,
she is good at riding and shooting.

773
00:32:45,220 --> 00:32:46,460
And she is good-looking.

774
00:32:47,220 --> 00:32:48,250
Therefore, I guess

775
00:32:49,050 --> 00:32:50,900
you would appreciate a girl like her.

776
00:32:54,140 --> 00:32:56,500
Why do you start
to guess this kind of stuff?

777
00:32:58,660 --> 00:32:59,380
It reminds me.

778
00:33:00,050 --> 00:33:02,050
Is there any man you fall for?

779
00:33:04,090 --> 00:33:06,660
I like painting, doing calligraphy
and reading poetry most of the time.

780
00:33:06,940 --> 00:33:09,090
I don’t have the time to pay attention
to any man.

781
00:33:11,050 --> 00:33:11,850
That’s true.

782
00:33:12,220 --> 00:33:13,530
Except for Count Cheng’an,

783
00:33:14,700 --> 00:33:16,250
there seems to be no one

784
00:33:17,610 --> 00:33:18,810
who is good enough for you.

785
00:33:24,940 --> 00:33:25,810
<i>Mingyue House</i>
Get out!

786
00:33:25,810 --> 00:33:26,530
<i>Mingyue House</i>
Don’t touch me!

787
00:33:26,530 --> 00:33:27,610
<i>Mingyue House</i>

788
00:33:27,610 --> 00:33:28,700
<i>Mingyue House</i>
A man like you

789
00:33:28,770 --> 00:33:30,900
doesn’t deserve to be our customer!

790
00:33:32,570 --> 00:33:33,420
Where are my new clothes?

791
00:33:33,900 --> 00:33:34,810
New clothes?

792
00:33:35,050 --> 00:33:36,900
They were used to pay for the room.

793
00:33:37,140 --> 00:33:38,740
Those are personal items
given to me by the Ban family.

794
00:33:38,740 --> 00:33:39,900
How can you take them?

795
00:33:40,330 --> 00:33:42,330
Your clothes? In your dream!

796
00:33:42,330 --> 00:33:44,140
Get out! Don’t affect our business!

797
00:33:44,330 --> 00:33:45,180
What is that attitude?

798
00:33:45,460 --> 00:33:46,940
I ranked third in the examination!

799
00:33:47,570 --> 00:33:49,010
Who cares what you ranked?

800
00:33:49,420 --> 00:33:51,460
I think you are just a joke!

801
00:33:51,900 --> 00:33:53,330
He is just a joke!

802
00:33:54,180 --> 00:33:55,180
Yeah.

803
00:33:57,770 --> 00:33:58,740
Wait.

804
00:33:59,500 --> 00:34:01,010
I will make great achievement

805
00:34:01,050 --> 00:34:03,980
and make all of you
kneel down to beg me!

806
00:34:04,810 --> 00:34:05,330
I...!

807
00:34:06,570 --> 00:34:07,380
Sisters!

808
00:34:07,380 --> 00:34:08,770
Let’s teach this unfaithful man
a lesson!

809
00:34:08,810 --> 00:34:10,530
Hit him! Hit him!

810
00:34:11,570 --> 00:34:12,290
Hit him!

811
00:34:14,090 --> 00:34:14,570
Get out!

812
00:34:16,780 --> 00:34:17,340
Hit him!

813
00:34:17,340 --> 00:34:18,570
Hit him! Hit him to death!

814
00:34:19,010 --> 00:34:20,210
Hit him!

815
00:34:22,900 --> 00:34:24,050
Hit him!

816
00:34:24,050 --> 00:34:25,210
Hit him!

817
00:34:25,210 --> 00:34:25,820
Hit him!

818
00:34:25,820 --> 00:34:27,860
Miss Li! Help!

819
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:37,340
